#Short Description
The WHEREDIDITGO smart contract on the Stellar network, written in Soroban, manages the issuance and redemption of vouchers for merchants or non-profits.
It ensures the safe transfer of tokens between parties, the transparency of voucher management, and the implementation of redemption regulations.
The process is auditable, fully decentralized, and on-chain.
